1
00:00:00,770 --> 00:00:02,800
Previously on Fairy Tail:

2
00:00:02,800 --> 00:00:07,310
Even before the qualifier, there was 
something between us and Sabertooth,

3
00:00:07,560 --> 00:00:12,700
but Natsu had to make it worse by 
slugging it out with them at their inn.

4
00:00:12,700 --> 00:00:15,120
They started somethin' right 
when we were gettin' momentum...

5
00:00:15,120 --> 00:00:17,580
Jeez. You never think ahead!

6
00:00:18,180 --> 00:00:21,660
By the way, it's almost the fourth 
day of the Grand Magic Games, right?

7
00:00:21,660 --> 00:00:23,410
Wendy got a tie,

8
00:00:23,410 --> 00:00:27,030
but Erza, Cana, and Laxus were awesome!

9
00:00:27,030 --> 00:00:29,800
I wonder what the next 
competition part will be.

10
00:00:29,800 --> 00:00:32,780
I've kind of got a bad feeling about this...

11
00:02:07,140 --> 00:02:08,600
Cheers!

12
00:02:08,600 --> 00:02:11,050
Today felt great!

13
00:02:11,050 --> 00:02:12,290
Aye!

14
00:02:12,290 --> 00:02:16,010
This isn't the guild, 
so don't break anything!

15
00:02:16,010 --> 00:02:18,330
Did you see my true power out there?

16
00:02:18,330 --> 00:02:20,490
That was a cheat, wasn't it?

17
00:02:20,490 --> 00:02:23,180
Gray-sama, you were wonderful 
today, as always!

18
00:02:23,180 --> 00:02:25,560
I didn't do anything...

19
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:28,720
I feel bad. Even though 
Erza-san had an easy victory,

20
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:31,200
I didn't win...

21
00:02:31,200 --> 00:02:33,840
What are you saying?! You did a good job!

22
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:35,940
You surprised everyone.

23
00:02:35,940 --> 00:02:38,220
Yeah! You were great, Wendy!

24
00:02:39,150 --> 00:02:42,530
At any rate, you've got amazing 
recuperative strength, Erza.

25
00:02:43,030 --> 00:02:45,890
That's thanks to Wendy and Poluchka-san.

26
00:02:46,370 --> 00:02:50,050
Even with their power, 
Elfman hasn't recovered...

27
00:02:50,050 --> 00:02:52,150
It's pathetic...

28
00:02:54,700 --> 00:02:56,390
Dammit...

29
00:02:56,390 --> 00:03:00,050
Somebody must be talkin' 
about me being a Man...

30
00:03:04,730 --> 00:03:08,510
Why is Ever sleepin' here?! Dammit!

31
00:03:10,890 --> 00:03:15,330
I'm not... worried about you...

32
00:03:17,730 --> 00:03:19,700
Don't tell me...

33
00:03:19,700 --> 00:03:21,160
...this woman's been here...

34
00:03:25,490 --> 00:03:26,650
...all this time...

35
00:03:30,190 --> 00:03:31,860
Naval Battle!

36
00:03:34,780 --> 00:03:36,950
Booze barrel surfing!

37
00:03:36,950 --> 00:03:38,300
Aye, sir!

38
00:03:38,300 --> 00:03:39,400
L-Look out!

39
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:40,580
Cut it out, Natsu!

40
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:44,580
What are you doin', jackass?!

41
00:03:45,060 --> 00:03:46,600
You wanna do it, too?!

42
00:03:46,600 --> 00:03:48,250
You're doin' it to the point 
of gettin' motion sick?!

43
00:03:48,490 --> 00:03:50,040
Alright! I'll do it!

44
00:03:51,630 --> 00:03:54,220
Do your best, Gray-sama!

45
00:03:55,220 --> 00:03:57,220
What the hell is with your clothes?!

46
00:03:57,740 --> 00:03:58,760
In that case...

47
00:03:59,630 --> 00:04:01,130
...I'm up next!

48
00:04:01,130 --> 00:04:02,470
Yeesh! It's dangerous, I said!

49
00:04:02,470 --> 00:04:04,430
Somebody, stop them!

50
00:04:05,100 --> 00:04:07,850
Everyone, you're getting too excited!

51
00:04:07,850 --> 00:04:09,850
Lu-chan, why don't you join in?

52
00:04:09,850 --> 00:04:11,680
I'm wearing a skirt, after all...

53
00:04:12,900 --> 00:04:16,940
I see someone over there who 
wiped out wearing a skirt...

54
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:24,700
Even now, when I close my 
eyes, I can picture it...

55
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:27,570
...Lu-chan...

56
00:04:27,570 --> 00:04:29,230
Here you go, Lisanna!

57
00:04:29,230 --> 00:04:31,500
Everyone reveling, singing...

58
00:04:32,770 --> 00:04:34,160
...eating, dancing...

59
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:38,170
...on the jubilant third night.

60
00:04:47,050 --> 00:04:48,500
Sting-kun...

61
00:04:48,980 --> 00:04:50,680
Can't you sleep?

62
00:04:51,250 --> 00:04:52,310
Lector...

63
00:04:55,130 --> 00:04:58,200
I have a feeling that I'm going 
to fight Natsu-san tomorrow.

64
00:04:59,520 --> 00:05:01,930
I've been waiting for that day...

65
00:05:02,520 --> 00:05:03,770
...for seven years...

66
00:05:05,510 --> 00:05:08,180
I know you'll win, Sting-kun!

67
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:36,230
Both you and Kagura have been 
acting weird since we got back.

68
00:05:36,990 --> 00:05:38,650
Did something happen?

69
00:05:40,630 --> 00:05:41,790
It's not important...

70
00:05:44,960 --> 00:05:47,530
Why is Jellal with Fairy Tail?

71
00:05:48,790 --> 00:05:50,920
Does Er-chan know this?

72
00:05:52,330 --> 00:05:54,930
If there's something weighing on your mind,

73
00:05:55,420 --> 00:05:56,670
tell me what it is.

74
00:05:57,180 --> 00:06:00,040
After all, we're teammates.

75
00:06:00,340 --> 00:06:03,450
Thank you. But I'm fine.

76
00:06:03,450 --> 00:06:05,680
It has nothing to do with the matches.

77
00:06:08,010 --> 00:06:10,160
H-Hey... Hey...

78
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:11,980
Let's definitely win this thing!

79
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:16,100
I love this guild,

80
00:06:16,450 --> 00:06:20,420
so I want to work even harder for everyone!

81
00:06:45,330 --> 00:06:47,170
Sergeant Yukino Agria.

82
00:06:47,840 --> 00:06:49,320
Please pardon my unannounced visit.

83
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:53,050
While various feelings crossed each other,

84
00:06:53,730 --> 00:06:56,250
the third night of the tournament wore on.

85
00:07:01,100 --> 00:07:04,480
We were heading for that day.

86
00:07:05,900 --> 00:07:07,400
We had four days...

87
00:07:08,090 --> 00:07:10,560
...until that fateful day.

88
00:07:17,650 --> 00:07:20,370
Day four of the Grand Magic Games!

89
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:24,320
In just a moment, today's 
competition will begin!

90
00:07:24,990 --> 00:07:27,750
The name of the competition is "Naval Battle"!

91
00:07:27,750 --> 00:07:31,300
In other words, a sea battle!

92
00:07:31,750 --> 00:07:35,850
Any player who leaves the 
sphere of water is out!

93
00:07:35,850 --> 00:07:38,640
The last person to remain 
in the sphere is the winner!

94
00:07:39,890 --> 00:07:42,300
However, when it gets 
down to two people left,

95
00:07:42,300 --> 00:07:44,480
a special rule will come into effect.

96
00:07:45,540 --> 00:07:48,100
That's the five-minute rule!

97
00:07:48,100 --> 00:07:50,000
When there are two players 
left, they've got five minutes!

98
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:54,820
The one person who leaves the sphere 
during that time will be in last place.

99
00:07:55,180 --> 00:07:58,470
So it's basically a sumo match in water.

100
00:07:58,470 --> 00:08:02,050
I can't wait! Thank you 
very much for inviting me!

101
00:08:02,490 --> 00:08:06,550
Our guest today is Rabian-san, leader 
of the Scheherazade Theatrical Troupe.

102
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:10,700
All of the teams are entering the water.

103
00:08:10,700 --> 00:08:12,950
Cheria from Lamia Scale!

104
00:08:13,650 --> 00:08:16,970
I tied yesterday, but I'll 
try even harder today!

105
00:08:18,950 --> 00:08:21,290
Jenny from Blue Pegasus!

106
00:08:21,860 --> 00:08:24,190
There's no way I'll lose this time!

107
00:08:26,610 --> 00:08:28,990
From Mermaid Heel, Risley!

108
00:08:29,500 --> 00:08:32,280
Better not underestimate a mermaid!

109
00:08:33,100 --> 00:08:36,650
Juvia from Fairy Tail B has 
also entered the water!

110
00:08:36,650 --> 00:08:38,330
Juvia <i>is</i> the water.

111
00:08:38,650 --> 00:08:40,740
This is Juvia's exclusive territory.

112
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:50,700
Sabertooth's Minerva has arrived.

113
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:56,340
There she is... Minerva! 
Listen to those cheers!

114
00:08:56,340 --> 00:09:00,590
Sabertooth certainly did choose 
their top five strongest to compete.

115
00:09:00,590 --> 00:09:02,810
Thank you very much!

116
00:09:03,730 --> 00:09:07,130
And Lucy from Fairy Tail A!

117
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:09,670
I can't lose either!

118
00:09:09,670 --> 00:09:12,690
I have to redeem myself after 
blowing it on the first day!

119
00:09:13,370 --> 00:09:16,640
What a gorgeous tapestry we've got before us!

120
00:09:16,640 --> 00:09:19,700
All of the players are female 
and they're wearing swimsuits!

121
00:09:19,700 --> 00:09:24,030
Thank you very much! Thank you 
very much! Thank you very much!

122
00:09:24,030 --> 00:09:25,280
Um...

123
00:09:25,770 --> 00:09:28,460
I'm here, too... and I'm wild.

124
00:09:29,280 --> 00:09:30,700
A man?

125
00:09:30,700 --> 00:09:32,050
You clucked your tongue at me?!

126
00:09:32,810 --> 00:09:36,200
The rules are simple. If you 
leave the water, you're out.

127
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:39,680
In just a moment, the 
Naval Battle will begin!

128
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:49,550
Go get 'em, Lucy!

129
00:09:49,550 --> 00:09:52,470
Since she's in water, she 
can use Aquarius, right?

130
00:09:52,470 --> 00:09:54,460
This is a good contest for her.

131
00:09:54,460 --> 00:09:55,320
Yep!

132
00:09:55,640 --> 00:09:59,270
I think this match is Juvia's to lose.

133
00:09:59,270 --> 00:10:00,900
I dunno...

134
00:10:00,900 --> 00:10:05,360
Lucy can use plenty of other 
Celestial Spirits beyond Aquarius.

135
00:10:05,360 --> 00:10:08,520
We probably shouldn't make 
light of Mermaid Heel either.

136
00:10:08,770 --> 00:10:11,500
After all, they do have 
"mermaid" in their name.

137
00:10:11,500 --> 00:10:15,610
That Minerva looks like 
a tough customer, too...

138
00:10:15,610 --> 00:10:17,720
Lu-chan, do your best!

139
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:22,430
And now, let the Naval Battle begin!

140
00:10:22,970 --> 00:10:25,540
Sorry, everyone, but right off the bat...

141
00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:28,180
Open! Gate of the Water Bearer!

142
00:10:28,890 --> 00:10:30,180
Aquarius!

143
00:10:32,210 --> 00:10:33,060
A Celestial Spirit!

144
00:10:34,280 --> 00:10:37,490
They've got a mermaid, too, 
huh? The more the merrier!

145
00:10:39,540 --> 00:10:42,410
Water is my garden!

146
00:10:45,660 --> 00:10:47,400
Wild!

147
00:10:47,400 --> 00:10:50,130
Oh, no, you don't! Water Cyclone!

148
00:10:53,860 --> 00:10:57,940
Aquarius and Juvia's attacks 
are colliding head on!

149
00:10:57,940 --> 00:10:59,700
We've got a highlight right away!

150
00:10:59,700 --> 00:11:02,800
Wow! I wonder which of them is stronger?!

151
00:11:03,100 --> 00:11:05,200
Good luck, Juvia!

152
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:07,880
After her, good luck to you, too, Lucy!

153
00:11:08,290 --> 00:11:11,640
And then, just a little 
bit of good luck to Jenny!

154
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:15,320
The way you cheer is a pain.

155
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:18,280
Well, who do you think is going to win?

156
00:11:18,810 --> 00:11:20,330
It's not even worth asking.

157
00:11:20,800 --> 00:11:23,740
You let Juvia into water, 
nobody else stands a chance.

158
00:11:25,700 --> 00:11:28,080
I haven't seen you for a while, Aquarius-san.

159
00:11:28,080 --> 00:11:31,180
Just because we're acquainted, 
don't think I'm gonna hold back.

160
00:11:31,180 --> 00:11:32,580
You took the words out of my mouth.

161
00:11:32,980 --> 00:11:35,620
Aquarius really is amazing, huh?

162
00:11:35,620 --> 00:11:38,080
I mean, she's not even takin' 
a licking from Juvia's power!

163
00:11:38,340 --> 00:11:39,530
But by that same argument,

164
00:11:39,530 --> 00:11:43,220
I get the feeling that Juvia-san's 
amazing for not losing to Aquarius-san!

165
00:11:44,800 --> 00:11:45,850
We're even?!

166
00:11:46,060 --> 00:11:47,290
Juvia is going to win!

167
00:11:47,640 --> 00:11:51,450
Juvia can't let Gray-sama see 
her shameful in battle!

168
00:11:53,230 --> 00:11:56,660
It seems Juvia is worried 
about how you see her.

169
00:11:59,110 --> 00:12:02,300
You must realize by now 
how Juvia feels about you.

170
00:12:03,020 --> 00:12:04,700
Why not give her a clear-cut response?

171
00:12:12,150 --> 00:12:13,270
Juvia!

172
00:12:13,270 --> 00:12:14,690
My romantic rival!

173
00:12:14,690 --> 00:12:16,460
You've got me all wrong!

174
00:12:19,310 --> 00:12:20,830
What kind of fight is this?!

175
00:12:21,290 --> 00:12:24,000
The toughest opponents are 
taking each other out.

176
00:12:24,400 --> 00:12:26,830
In that case, while I've got the chance...

177
00:12:30,950 --> 00:12:32,190
I'll start with one!

178
00:12:32,190 --> 00:12:34,980
Wild!

179
00:12:36,300 --> 00:12:38,400
Quatro Puppy is out!

180
00:12:38,610 --> 00:12:41,530
He was sucker punched by Jenny!

181
00:12:41,530 --> 00:12:45,230
But only Quatro Puppy feels bad about that!

182
00:12:45,230 --> 00:12:48,730
This crowd only cares about the girls!

183
00:12:48,730 --> 00:12:52,750
Thank you very much! Thank you 
very much! Thank you very much!

184
00:12:52,750 --> 00:12:56,090
What was the point of me 
being in there anyway?

185
00:12:56,430 --> 00:12:59,430
That woman's cheap tricks know no bounds.

186
00:13:00,470 --> 00:13:03,260
That kind of fighting is Jenny all over.

187
00:13:03,260 --> 00:13:05,900
You know, that wasn't a compliment...

188
00:13:06,840 --> 00:13:08,960
I've gotta do my best, too!

189
00:13:16,270 --> 00:13:18,730
Never underestimate the chubby!

190
00:13:22,690 --> 00:13:24,860
We'll never get anywhere at this rate!

191
00:13:24,860 --> 00:13:26,300
I'm going back for now!

192
00:13:26,300 --> 00:13:28,000
Wha? Why?!

193
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:31,140
In water, you're the one 
I can count on the most!

194
00:13:32,090 --> 00:13:33,150
I've got a date!

195
00:13:33,150 --> 00:13:34,830
Hey!

196
00:13:34,830 --> 00:13:36,000
Oh, my!

197
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:39,680
The Celestial Spirit, Aquarius, 
left to go on a date!

198
00:13:39,680 --> 00:13:41,450
She is a girl...

199
00:13:41,450 --> 00:13:42,710
Boring...

200
00:13:45,930 --> 00:13:47,140
You're wide open!

201
00:13:47,140 --> 00:13:49,590
This is my chance to take 
out my romantic rival!

202
00:13:52,810 --> 00:13:54,720
Virgo! Aries!

203
00:13:59,650 --> 00:14:02,780
I'm sorry this is so fluffy!

204
00:14:04,730 --> 00:14:07,050
I'm your sexy guard, Princess!

205
00:14:08,350 --> 00:14:10,180
That was close...

206
00:14:11,900 --> 00:14:14,100
Thank you very much!

207
00:14:14,100 --> 00:14:17,040
No matter how many you bring 
out, the result is the same!

208
00:14:17,810 --> 00:14:20,280
Virgo, Aries, do your best!

209
00:14:20,660 --> 00:14:25,130
I'm better on land than in the water...

210
00:14:25,130 --> 00:14:27,090
...but I'll try my best!

211
00:14:31,720 --> 00:14:34,170
I've gotta do my best to impress, too!

212
00:14:34,880 --> 00:14:37,080
Then give me your best shot!

213
00:14:39,020 --> 00:14:41,480
Don't forget about me either!

214
00:14:41,480 --> 00:14:42,850
Cheria!

215
00:14:42,850 --> 00:14:45,270
Fairy Tail's Wendy-tan!

216
00:14:45,270 --> 00:14:47,270
It looks like she wants to 
get in on the action, too!

217
00:14:47,850 --> 00:14:50,250
Well, her match did end in a draw yesterday.

218
00:14:50,690 --> 00:14:55,270
She's as good as saying, "This time for sure,
 I want to beat Cheria with my own hands!"

219
00:14:55,790 --> 00:14:58,040
I'm not thinking that at all!

220
00:14:58,290 --> 00:15:02,080
I wanted to see Wendy-tan fight...

221
00:15:02,320 --> 00:15:07,130
Thank you very much for 
helping my troupe last time!

222
00:15:07,520 --> 00:15:09,000
Fairy Tail A!

223
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:12,510
Why didn't you let Wendy-tan do this one?!

224
00:15:12,730 --> 00:15:15,010
It's not too late! Switch her in!

225
00:15:15,010 --> 00:15:16,680
Thank you very much.

226
00:15:16,680 --> 00:15:17,930
Shut up!

227
00:15:18,370 --> 00:15:20,650
Juiva is going to knock you all out at once!

228
00:15:20,650 --> 00:15:24,240
Nobody can win against Juvia in the water!

229
00:15:25,560 --> 00:15:28,610
Juvia learned this move when 
Second Origin was released...

230
00:15:28,610 --> 00:15:30,400
This new special technique!

231
00:15:30,760 --> 00:15:32,950
Go forth, wings of love!

232
00:15:33,310 --> 00:15:35,230
Gray-sama, love!

233
00:15:37,320 --> 00:15:39,420
Knock it off!

234
00:15:53,500 --> 00:15:56,250
Fluffy guard at full throttle!

235
00:15:56,250 --> 00:15:57,970
Princess, hang on!

236
00:15:57,970 --> 00:16:02,780
Would you believe it?! Juvia 
has knocked out three at once!

237
00:16:04,410 --> 00:16:08,430
In a water battle, Juvia is unbeatable!

238
00:16:09,300 --> 00:16:13,110
I wasn't able to muster as much 
power as I thought in the water...

239
00:16:13,390 --> 00:16:15,820
You gave it your all, Cheria!

240
00:16:16,640 --> 00:16:20,580
Did you feel something while 
watching Juvia, Gray-sama?

241
00:16:25,980 --> 00:16:27,220
He's totally turned off!

242
00:16:31,340 --> 00:16:32,740
Juvia!

243
00:16:34,840 --> 00:16:37,760
She was outstanding, but 
unfortunately, she's out!

244
00:16:37,760 --> 00:16:39,560
But even so, for third place,

245
00:16:39,560 --> 00:16:41,720
her team gets six points!

246
00:16:41,720 --> 00:16:43,180
That idiot...

247
00:16:43,180 --> 00:16:44,790
She went out of the sphere.

248
00:16:44,790 --> 00:16:47,360
Why? Was she not paying attention?

249
00:16:49,430 --> 00:16:51,150
Our lady is a mischievous one.

250
00:16:51,620 --> 00:16:56,640
With her magic, she should've been able to 
get them all out of the sphere in an instant.

251
00:16:56,640 --> 00:16:58,980
She's already won this.

252
00:17:01,110 --> 00:17:03,600
Only Minerva and Lucy are left.

253
00:17:03,600 --> 00:17:06,670
Lucy's Celestial Spirits 
have gone home for now.

254
00:17:06,950 --> 00:17:10,780
To avoid depleting her magic and 
physical strength, most likely.

255
00:17:10,780 --> 00:17:16,020
Alright! Who's gonna win this, 
Sabertooth or Fairy Tail?!

256
00:17:18,320 --> 00:17:21,100
The five-minute rule comes into play now!

257
00:17:21,100 --> 00:17:25,990
The person who leaves the sphere in the 
next five minutes will be in last place!

258
00:17:26,540 --> 00:17:28,770
I wonder what this rule is for...

259
00:17:28,770 --> 00:17:32,150
It's to keep the tension 
high to the very end.

260
00:17:32,150 --> 00:17:33,820
Thank you very much.

261
00:17:34,550 --> 00:17:39,950
With my magic, I could have you 
outside of here in a flash,

262
00:17:39,950 --> 00:17:42,880
but that would spoil the fun.

263
00:17:43,320 --> 00:17:46,920
Try to withstand this, Fairy Tail.

264
00:17:50,220 --> 00:17:51,540
What is that?!

265
00:17:56,110 --> 00:17:57,020
Heat?

266
00:17:57,350 --> 00:17:58,380
In the water?!

267
00:18:00,440 --> 00:18:01,620
Lucy!

268
00:18:01,620 --> 00:18:04,000
What the hell kind of magic is that?!

269
00:18:07,700 --> 00:18:10,050
Th-That time it was heavy...

270
00:18:10,360 --> 00:18:11,840
Felt like lead...

271
00:18:12,170 --> 00:18:14,200
If I don't get a Celestial Spirit out here...

272
00:18:16,030 --> 00:18:18,550
Huh? Where are my keys?!

273
00:18:24,790 --> 00:18:26,190
When did she...?!

274
00:18:34,320 --> 00:18:38,280
If Lucy exits the sphere now, 
she'll be in last place!

275
00:18:46,190 --> 00:18:47,260
Oh?

276
00:18:54,970 --> 00:18:56,280
It's hot again!

277
00:18:56,670 --> 00:18:58,100
Feels like I'll get burned!

278
00:18:58,100 --> 00:18:59,570
Lucy!

279
00:18:59,570 --> 00:19:02,360
She can't use any magic with her keys stolen!

280
00:19:04,250 --> 00:19:05,370
No matter what...

281
00:19:08,680 --> 00:19:10,370
...kind of attack you throw at me...

282
00:19:13,340 --> 00:19:14,230
...I'm gonna...

283
00:19:14,750 --> 00:19:15,660
...take it!

284
00:19:19,070 --> 00:19:22,590
Maybe it's about time for 
me to put you outside?

285
00:19:24,450 --> 00:19:27,680
If I lose now...

286
00:19:29,280 --> 00:19:32,870
...I won't be able to face everyone...

287
00:19:32,870 --> 00:19:34,770
...who got me here!

288
00:19:39,400 --> 00:19:42,980
I can't betray everyone's feelings!

289
00:19:43,620 --> 00:19:44,610
That's why...

290
00:19:45,940 --> 00:19:48,480
...there's no way I'm gonna give up!

291
00:19:57,850 --> 00:20:00,470
W-What's going on here?!

292
00:20:00,470 --> 00:20:02,650
Minerva's attacks have stopped!

293
00:20:03,450 --> 00:20:05,490
And just like that...

294
00:20:06,320 --> 00:20:07,680
...the five minutes are up!

295
00:20:07,680 --> 00:20:08,680
Yes!

296
00:20:09,400 --> 00:20:12,270
All that's left is ranking them!

297
00:20:27,350 --> 00:20:28,530
Lucy!

298
00:20:30,330 --> 00:20:32,950
You're arrogant, Fairy Tail!

299
00:20:33,260 --> 00:20:35,830
What do you know of us?!

300
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:40,290
We are this world's number one guild!

301
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:43,340
We're Sabertooth!

302
00:20:47,400 --> 00:20:49,720
This time for sure she's going out...

303
00:20:50,410 --> 00:20:51,390
She vanished?!

304
00:20:55,850 --> 00:20:58,060
Lucy was going to be knocked 
out of the sphere...

305
00:20:58,060 --> 00:20:59,980
...but somehow, she's appeared 
in front of Minerva!

306
00:20:59,980 --> 00:21:01,720
Is it that woman's magic?!

307
00:21:01,720 --> 00:21:03,780
Why would she bother bringing her back?

308
00:21:03,780 --> 00:21:05,550
Does she intend to rough Lucy up?!

309
00:21:05,550 --> 00:21:07,330
The match is already over!

310
00:21:08,420 --> 00:21:10,310
And now a body blow!

311
00:21:10,310 --> 00:21:14,330
Even without using magic, 
Minerva has incredible power!

312
00:21:16,450 --> 00:21:19,000
Please stop. Now you're just being cruel.

313
00:21:19,230 --> 00:21:21,860
Thank you very much!

314
00:21:21,860 --> 00:21:24,470
She's still in the water, so she's not down!

315
00:21:24,470 --> 00:21:27,250
She's just taking a beating!

316
00:21:27,720 --> 00:21:30,430
Stop!!

317
00:21:33,010 --> 00:21:35,100
Sabertooth!

318
00:21:35,700 --> 00:21:40,150
Do you know what it means to dis Sabertooth?

319
00:21:40,150 --> 00:21:42,940
I'm going to teach you with her body!

320
00:21:43,530 --> 00:21:46,880
Stop this! She'll destroy 
the Celestial Spirit wizard!

321
00:21:47,600 --> 00:21:49,280
Stop the competition!

322
00:21:50,850 --> 00:21:53,250
The referee has stopped it!

323
00:21:53,250 --> 00:21:55,260
The competition is over!

324
00:21:55,620 --> 00:21:57,490
The winner is Minerva!

325
00:21:57,490 --> 00:22:00,290
Sabertooth really is strong!

326
00:22:00,850 --> 00:22:04,790
Lucy hasn't moved for a 
while, but is she okay?!

327
00:22:06,300 --> 00:22:07,650
Lucy!

328
00:22:19,510 --> 00:22:21,880
Lucy!!

329
00:23:55,970 --> 00:23:56,870
At last!

330
00:23:56,870 --> 00:24:00,040
The identity of that weird rabbit is...

331
00:24:02,290 --> 00:24:03,350
<i>That person?!</i>

332
00:24:03,350 --> 00:24:07,840
Hey, Natsu, when is it you say 
the words "I feel sick"?

333
00:24:07,840 --> 00:24:09,020
Where's that question coming from?

334
00:24:09,020 --> 00:24:10,950
Anyway, I guess I say it 
when I have motion sickness.

335
00:24:10,950 --> 00:24:12,080
What other situation?

336
00:24:12,080 --> 00:24:13,470
Like when I eat too much?

337
00:24:13,930 --> 00:24:16,470
Next time: The Perfume I Dedicate to You!

338
00:24:16,830 --> 00:24:18,800
You don't use it with people?

339
00:24:18,800 --> 00:24:19,860
Uh-uh.

340
00:24:19,860 --> 00:24:24,200
I see... Then I've got a feeling 
I can't put into words...

